Package com.gemalto.riskengine

Class GAHErrorCodes

java.lang.Object
com.gemalto.riskengine.GAHErrorCodes
public final class GAHErrorCodes extends Object
This class holds the possible error codes by GAHRiskEngine when failed to prefetch signals or failed to get VisitID. These error codes and error messages will be posted in error() callback in GAHResponseCallback interface or from onPrefetchCompleted() callback in GAHPrefetchStatusCallback interface.
Since:
2.0.0
